# 📜 Real-Time MIDI Notation — Dual License (MIT + Apache 2.0)  
### Version 3.0.0 — Combined Open License Model

Starting from **version 3.0.0**, the Real-Time MIDI Notation project is released under a **dual-license model**:

# ✔ MIT License  
# ✔ Apache License 2.0  

Users and developers may choose **either** license depending on their needs.

This model provides:

- maximum freedom (MIT)  
- strong legal protection (Apache 2.0)  
- patent safety (Apache 2.0)  
- compatibility with commercial and open‑source projects  
- long‑term sustainability for research and industry  

